         MACRO                                                                  
&L       PFLIP                                                                  
.*       Changed from subroutine to inline code.  4/92, Niz                     
&L       ST    R15,@R13                                                         
         L     R15,CVCURJCB                                                     
         WITH  (JCB,R15),BEGIN                                                  
         FLIP  (JCBPTA,JCBPTB)                                                  
         FLIP  (PAR,PBR)                                                        
         END                                                                    
         L     R15,@R13                                                         
         MEND                                                                   
